author: Jackie Borchardt, cleveland.com
title: Ohio taxpayers spent $1.3 million on TV ads featuring Josh Mandel, Urban Meyer
text: Ohio Treasurer Josh Mandel spent more than $1.3 million in tax dollars on TV advertisements featuring himself and Ohio State football coach Urban Meyer, promoting a new investment program for Ohioans with disabilities.
